%^BOLD%^%^BLACK%^%^ULINE%^Shadow Mystery%^RESET%^

The shadows comfort and console you against the glaring light.

%^CYAN%^BOLD%^Revelations:%^RESET%^
( 1) Cloak of Darkness  : Innate ability
( 5) Wings of Darkness  : Innate ability
(10) Dark Secrets       : 10% void resistance
(15) Pierce the Shadows : Permanent passive darkvision
(21) Shadow Mastery     : +1 to spell level for shadow illusion spells
(31) Final Revelation   : Fast healing 1, 10% cold resistance, immunity to critical hits while in darkness

%^BOLD%^%^BLACK%^Class Skills%^RESET%^: influence, stealth, academics

%^BOLD%^%^BLACK%^Bonus Spells%^RESET%^: blur, invisibility, deeper darkness, shadow necromancy, vampiric shadow shield, shadow alteration, mass invisibility, greater shadow evocation, shades
